prodNameC: 羅氏免疫分析弓漿蟲免疫球蛋白 G 抗體檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
PreciControl Toxo IgG
Reagents - working solutions
？PC TOXIGG1: 8 bottles, each containing 1.0 mL of control serum Human serum, negative to low positive for Toxo IgG antibodies (approx. 1 IU/mL); preservative.
？PC TOXIGG2: 8 bottles, each containing 1.0 mL of control serum Human serum, positive for anti-Toxo IgG antibodies (approx. 50 IU/mL); preservative.

Toxo IgG
Reagents - working solutions
M  Streptavidin-coated microparticles (transparent cap), 1 bottle, 6.5 mL: Streptavidin-coated microparticles, 0.72 mg/mL; preservative. 
R1  Toxoplasma-Ag~biotin (gray cap), 1 bottle, 9 mL: Biotinylated T. gondii-specific antigen (recombinant, E. coli), > 400 μg/L, Tris buffer 50 mmol/L, pH 7.5; preservative.
R2  Toxoplasma-Ag~Ru(bpy)2+3 (black cap), bottle, 9 mL: T. gondii-specific antigen (recombinant, E. coli) labeled with ruthenium complex > 400 μg/L; TRIS buffer 50 mmol/L, pH 7.5; preservative.
Cal1 Negative calibrator 1 (white cap), 2 bottles of 1.0 mL each: Human serum, non-reactive for anti-Toxoplasma IgG; buffer; preservative.
Cal2 Positive calibrator 2 (black cap), 2 bottles of 1.0 mL each: Human serum, reactive for anti-Toxoplasma IgG, approx. 100 IU/mL; buffer; preservative.
